posts.post_content:
The remaining 64 cards below are also sold, in addition to the 11 cards previously sold.  Thanks to everyone who had interest in the cards.

T206 cards below range from PR to VGEX, and are priced accordingly in tiers.  All cards are new to the hobby.  Email for larger scans or with any questions.  First person to indicate “I’ll take it” will secure a card/cards.  Two cards are punched, as indicated below.  Additional cards have writing on the front, also indicated below.  Check / m.o. or paypal gift preferred.  I will cover shipping.  Thanks for looking,

Andrew
